comment: Hello Kiu, really love to see more vlogs of your daily routine (the opportunity to see how a successful entrepreneur like you spend your daily life, it will be so motivating and enjoyable). I personally will prefer this over your haircut clips which are also nice. Hope to see more of your vlogs in future rather than just 1 week. Fighting, will cheer for you in future.

For anyone interested in filming, what he said about the equipment is true. Your camera doesn't need to be amazing. You're often better off investing in proper lighting than a better camera.
Unless you're going to have a great degree of editing the source footage, it is also better to look at stuff like contrast than resolution.

Good luck with your videos!
